    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and comparison against the predicate device using the relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1).",
